uten Urban Design und formuliert ein zeitgemäßes und zukunftsgewandtes Verständnis für die "Große Transformation".  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Sep 2021) 0aCity planning. 4aUrban Design, Stadtplanung, Transformation, Urbanismus.  aurban planning.  aurbanism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2020z9783110704679oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG0 cEPUBz97830356205800 cprintz978303562050440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303562057340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035620573423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035620573/original  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020